task.summary:
Made a Character Template, extension will be "tec" (TextEngineCharacter) Created the first 3 genders, which may be expanded upon, based on what the game will be about. Created the Jobs enum with the Type of Job, will be expanded upon. A basic Character class has been made. Created 3 handler files, still need to be made. Game.java exists, but is nothing.
This commit is just some easy thoughts I had, next step is to actually create the framework.
Made some structure changes. Wrote that damn README ting.
Moved some stuff again. Created the basics for the GUI. Tried something with CharacterHandler.java, but need to make a template/test character first.
Text now displays correctly. The GUI is now correctly displaying for now. Using a new interface Window.java to give all the windows a common method.
Buttons now have keys. Made the first try to get buttons to have new actions
Rename AbstractWindow.java to AbstractMainWindow.java. Added Choice.java, which will make the choices happen.
Made many structure changes. Introduced the .tes extension. Stories will be made using the Template.
Made the beginning of creating a choice.
Added the start of making sure that it can continue from a previous choice. A lot of TODOs added. Lots of unfinished shit. Everything still needs to be tested.
